       cd scripts; ./mkfjcore.sh; md5sum fjcore-X.Y.Z.tar.gz; cd ..
       9ea7c6cdb441217b84c3a9bab05ad658  fjcore-3.3.3.tar.gz

  do the release and announce it
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
